          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-black mb-3 group-hover:text-red transition-colors">Putting AI into Practice for Better Investment Returns</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Authored by Michael Salafia — explores how STAX integrates artificial intelligence into CRE underwriting, deal sourcing, and investment analysis to deliver better outcomes for gas station and NNN investors.</p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[13px] font-semibold text-red mt-4 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">Read article →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- CRE Secrets -->
        <a href="https://www.cresecrets.com/how-to-simplify-sale-leaseback-transactions-in-commercial-real-estate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group border border-black/8 rounded-xl p-8 bg-white hover:border-red hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="inline-block text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase bg-red-light text-red px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Expert Feature</span>
            <span class="text-[12px] text-gray-400 font-medium shrink-0">2024</span>
